headline: Fastenal Company to Host Investor Presentation
summary: WINONA, Minn., March 06, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq:FAST) (collectively referred to as 'Fastenal' or by terms such as 'we', 'our', or 'us') announced its intention to host an investor presentation on March 13, 2025 located in St. Paul, Minnesota, which will be available to access via webcast.
